DSHeader.description: Unlock the power of data with Connecting Dots Data Science course, mastering crucial skills for success in the field, all backed by secure placement support.

cards.title: What is Data Science?
cards.content: Data Science involves extracting actionable insights from raw data using various scientific methods, algorithms, and processes. It provides tools for working with data from diverse sources, including financial logs, multimedia files, and sensors.

cards.title: What does a Data Scientist do?
cards.content: A data scientist analyzes data to provide actionable insights for various processes. They possess strong statistical, analytical, and technical skills to work with structured and unstructured data.
listItems: Identify data sources and collect data.
Formulate strategies to solve business challenges.

cards.title: Why take Data Science training?
cards.content: Data scientists are in high demand across industries, making a Data Science certification valuable. Our training course is designed for both beginners and professionals to equip them with essential skills.

projects.name: Revealing the Power of Data
projects.description: Here, in Excel, you need to find the vital stats of the departments such as weak spots and bottlenecks in the processes, and find ways to scale them up.

projects.name: Human Resource Management System
projects.description: This application helps the student complete their HR toolkit with the secure management of tracking and delivering HR documents, organizing personal records, payroll data, etc.

projects.name: Vehicle Sales Analysis
projects.description: The idea behind introducing this project in our Data Science & Analytics with AI Certification course is to understand how to analyze and generate Vehicle Sales Report and dive into the data of ‘total vehicles sold’, ‘total revenue generated’, seasonality of the revenue and so on.

projects.name: Supply Chain & Logistics Analysis
projects.description: In the Data Science & Analytics with AI, students will have a project where they will have to evaluate every stage of a supply chain starting from the time the business acquires raw materials or supplies from its suppliers to the delivery of the final product to the consumers.

projects.name: Face Detection
projects.description: This is probably the most popular application of the computer vision. Therefore, in our Data Science & Analytics with AI Course, we teach the technology that finds applications in various industries, such as security and social media. Thus, we are building a face detection project through OpenCV.
